{"tid":2500762,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"會員貓貓懷孕(#29784)違反#4 假新聞、標題黨、#8 網路打手、分身帳號，請連仔做野","createTime":"2021-04-23T01:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-23T07:22:22.000Z","uid":281306,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cebc758702dda625442d5a1dfb244731bee44bc6","tid":2500762,"uid":281306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-23T01:47:17.000Z","msg":"有晒證據，請連仔做野<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">會員編號：29784<br />\n會員名稱：貓貓懷孕<br />\n註冊日期：2016年11月27日</span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">#4 假新聞、標題黨</span></span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">討論區機制：如有用戶為故意或多次發放假新聞故意誤導用戶或嘗試操控輿論，我們將作出禁言警告或永久封鎖處理。<br />\n違反原因：故意或多次發放假新聞故意誤導用戶或嘗試操控輿論</span><br />\n詳細來源：<br />\n連續兩日屈龍門告急 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2500662\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2500662</a> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/2499758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2499758</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">#8 網路打手、分身帳號</span></span><br />\n【１】<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">討論區機制：本討論區禁止使用分身帳號及所有網絡打手行為<br />\n違反原因：自認用兩個ac玩分化</span><br />\n詳細來源：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2409897/page/1?post=15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2409897/page/1?post=15</a><br />\n<br />\n【２】<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">討論區機制：絕不容許有人利用本討論區，有組織性或惡意煽動他人、操控輿論或達到個別目的。<br />\n違反原因：扮龍門打手，多次抄其他龍門食評po、出龍門fake news黎抹黑龍門，惡意煽動他人、操控輿論或達到個別目的</span><br />\n詳細來源：<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmU45rEk7mpgKYFLvtsHFaw6DGjT1kLSTKqFHieUusYBMC?filename=4Bk2FVN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Bk2FVN.png&h=c0b5f696&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ9cQxMujz6bttggynacP5zE7YPe5Gm11Vn6CCoNNEBme?filename=zsXXuO9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzsXXuO9.png&h=64861f9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c8d95f151e6ba3eb3d0b4c02e898b1ea141e5e4","tid":2500762,"uid":141668,"lik